    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 11. Head, frontal view: 1 – 5 — Campylomma celatum Wagner, 1969: 1 — male, holotype; 2 – 4 — female, paratype; 5 — male, paratype; 6 – 7 — Campylomma annulicorne (V. Signoret, 1865): 6 — female, 7 — male; 8 – 9 — Campylomma diversicorne Reuter, 1878: 8 — female, 9 — male; head, dorsal view 10 – 11 — Campylomma ochraceum (Scott, 1872): 10 — male; 11 — female." ;
